ing by Shirley Caesar on Apple Music|work=[[Apple Music]]|accessdate=April 22, 2020}}</ref><br><small>([[Shirley Caesar]] featuring the Clark Sisters)</small>\n| 1986\n| ''Christmasing''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Lift Every Voice and Sing]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/soul-exposed/1444045225|title=\t\nSoul Exposed by Melba Moore on Apple Music|work=[[Apple Music]]|accessdate=April 22, 2020}}</ref><br><small>([[Melba Moore]] featuring [[Gerald Albright]], [[Anita Baker]], [[Bobby Brown]], <br>[[Terri Lyne Carrington]], [[Karen Clark]], The Clark Sisters, [[Howard Hewett]], <br>[[Freddie Jackson]], [[Stephanie Mills]], Jeffrey Osbourne, Jake O, <br>[[Dionne Warwick]], [[BeBe & CeCe Winans]], [[Stevie Wonder]])</small><ref name=\"Melba\"/></small>\n| 1990\n| ''[[Soul Exposed]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lift Up Your Heads, O Ye Gates\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/handels-messiah-a-soulful-celebration/373802261|title=\t\nHandel's Messiah: A Soulful Celebration by Various Artists on Apple Music|work=[[Apple Music]]|accessdate=April 22, 2020}}</ref><br><small>([[Commissioned (gospel group)|Commissioned]])</small>\n| 1992\n| ''[[Handel's Messiah: A Soulful Celebration]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Nothing to Lose\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/2bpVDG20svJTW3F5eH01xj|title=\t\nTwinkie Clark-Terrell Presents \u00b7 The Florida A&M University Gospel Choir |work=[[Spotify]]|accessdate=April 22, 2020}}</ref><br><small>(The Florida A&M University Gospel Choir featuring the Clark Sisters)</small>\n| 1996\n| ''[[Twinkie Clark-Terrell]] Presents''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Jesus is a Love Song\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://music.apple.com/us/album/finally-karen/1444031474|title=\t\nFinally Karen by Karen Clark Sheard on Apple Music|work=[[Apple Music]]|accessdate=April 22, 2020}}</ref><br><small>([[Karen Clark-Sheard]] featuring the Clark Sisters)</small>\n| 1997\n| ''[[Finally Karen]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Pure G