 and producer known for his work in [[Bollywood]], and has also appeared in [[Tamil language|Tamil]], [[Marathi language|Marathi]], [[Kannada]], [[Malayalam]] and English language films.\n\n==Films==\n===Actor===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! Year !! Film !! Role !! Other notes \n|-\n| 1992 || ''[[Balwaan]]'' || Arjun Singh || \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1993 || ''[[Waqt Hamara Hai]]'' || Sunil Chaudhary ||\n|-\n|''[[Pehchaan (1993 film)|Pehchaan]]'' || Kunal Verma ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 1994 || ''[[Dilwale (1994 film)|Dilwale]]'' || Vikram Singh || Nominated\u2014[[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actor]]\n\n|-\n|''[[Anth]]'' || Vijay Saxena ||\n|-\n|''[[Mohra]]'' || Vishal Agnihotri ||\n|-\n|''[[Gopi Kishan]]'' || Gopi / Kishan || Double Role\n\n|-\n|''[[Hum Hain Bemisaal]]'' || Michael ||\n\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 1995 || ''[[Surakshaa (1995 film)|Surakshaa]]'' || Raja ||\n|-\n| ''Raghuveer (1995 film) |Raghuveer'' || Raghuveer ||\n|-\n|''[[Gaddaar (1995 film)|Gaddaar]]'' || Sunny ||\n|-\n|''[[Takkar (1995 film)|Takkar]]'' || Ravi Malhotra ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 1996 || ''[[Ek Tha Raja]]'' || Jay ||\n|-\n|''[[Vishwasghaat]]'' || Avinash ||\n|-\n|''[[Krishna (1996 Hindi film)|Krishna]]'' || Krishna / Sunil ||\n|-\n|''[[Shastra (1996 film)|Shastra]]'' || Vijay ||\n|-\n|''[[Sapoot]]'' || Raj Singhania ||\n|-\n|''[[Rakshak]]'' || Raj Sinha ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 1997 || ''[[Border (1997 film)|Border]]'' || Bhairav Singh || Nominated\u2014Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actor\n\n|-\n|''[[Prithvi (1997 film)|Prithvi]]'' || Prithvi ||\n|-\n|''[[Judge Mujrim]]'' || Sunil / Dhaga || Double Role\n\n|-\n|''[[Bhai (1997 film)|Bhai]]'' || Kundan ||\n|-\n|''[[Dhaal]]'' || Suraj ||\n|-\n|''[[Qahar]]'' || Amar Kapoor ||\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 1998 || ''[[Vinashak \u2013 Destroyer]]'' || Arjun Singh ||\n|-\n|''[[Aakrosh (1998 film)|Aakrosh]]'' || Dev Malhotra ||\n|-\n|''[[Humse Badhkar Kaun]]'' || Bhola / Suraj ||\n|-\n|''[[