arbour]] \n|\n|Mike Josey\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|'''[[Darrell Dexter]]'''\n|\n|[[Tony Ince]]\n|\n|Donna Toews\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Darrell Dexter]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Cole Harbour-Eastern Passage]]\n|\n|Lloyd Jackson\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Becky Kent]]\n|\n|Orest Ulan\n|\n|Denise Menard\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Becky Kent]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Dartmouth East]]\n|\n|Bert Thompson\n|\n|[[Joan Massey]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Andrew Younger]]\n|\n|Anna Mukpo\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Joan Massey]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Dartmouth North]]\n|\n|David Losey\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Trevor Zinck]]\n|\n|Jim Smith\n|\n|Alex Donaldson\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Trevor Zinck]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Dartmouth South-Portland Valley]]\n|\n|George Jordan\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Marilyn More]] \n|\n|Colin Hebb\n|\n|David Croft\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Marilyn More]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Eastern Shore (electoral district)|Eastern Shore]]\n|\n|[[Bill Dooks]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Sid Prest]]\n|\n|Loretta Halleran\n|\n|Michael Marshall\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Bill Dooks]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Preston (electoral district)|Preston]]\n|\n|Dwayne Provo\n|\n|Janet Sutcliffe\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Keith Colwell]]\n|\n|Sarah Densmore\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Keith Colwell]]\n|}\n\n===Central Nova===\n{{Canadian politics/candlist header|province=NS|PC|NDP|Liberal|Green|Independent}}\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Antigonish (provincial electoral district)|Antigonish]] \n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Angus MacIsaac]]\n|\n|[