adian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Cecil Clarke]] \n|\n|Russell MacDonald\n|\n|Ken Jardine\n|\n|Chris Milburn\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Cecil Clarke]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Cape Breton Nova]]\n|\n|Cory Hann\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Gordie Gosse]]\n|\n|Donnie Morrison\n|\n|Michael Milburn\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Gordie Gosse]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Cape Breton South (provincial electoral district)|Cape Breton South]]\n|\n|Steve Tobin\n|\n|Wayne McKay\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Manning MacDonald]]\n|\n|Cathy Theriault\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Manning MacDonald]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Cape Breton West]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Alfie MacLeod]]\n|\n|Delton MacDonald\n|\n|Josephine Kennedy\n|\n|Michael Parsons\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Alfie MacLeod]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Glace Bay (electoral district)|Glace Bay]]\n|\n|Tom MacPherson\n|\n|Myrtle Campbell\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[David Wilson (Canadian politician)|David Wilson]]\n|\n|Todd Pettigrew\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[David Wilson (Canadian politician)|David Wilson]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Inverness (provincial electoral district)|Inverness]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|'''[[Rodney MacDonald]]'''\n|\n|Michael MacIsaac\n|\n|Shaun Bennett\n|\n|Nathalie Arsenault\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Rodney MacDonald]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Richmond (Nova Scotia provincial electoral district)|Richmond]]\n|\n|John Greene\n|\n|Clair Rankin\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Michel Samson]]\n|\n|John Percy\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Michel Samson]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Victoria-The Lakes]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Keith Bain]]\n|\n|Fraser Patterson\n|\n|[[Gerald Sampson]]\n|\n|James V. O'Brien\n|\n|Stemer MacLeod\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Keith Bain]]\n|}\n\n==Opinion polls==\n{|Class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:85%;line-height:13px\"\n|- style=\"height:30px; background-color:#E9E9E9\"\n! style=\"width:100px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Date\n! style=\"width:200px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Source\n! style=\"width:70px;\"| [[Progressive Conservative Association of Nova Scotia|PC]]\n! style=\"width:70px;\"| [[Nova Scotia New Democratic Party|NDP]]\n! style=\"width:70px;\"| [[Nova Scotia Liberal Party|Liberal]]\n! style=\"width:70px;\"| [[Green Party of Nova Scotia|Green]]\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{Canadian party colour|NS|Green}};\"|\n|-\n| 4 Jun 2009\n| [http://www.angusreidstrategies.com/ Angus Reid Strategies]\n| 23\n| {{Party shading/NDP (Canada)}}| '''47'''\n| 26\n| 3\n|-\n| 1 Jun 2009\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20071213043931/http://www.cra.ca/en/home/Newsroom/default.aspx Corporate Research Associates]\n| 26\n| {{Party shading/NDP (Canada)}}| '''44'''\n| 28\n| 2\n|-\n| 7\u201316 May 2009\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20071213043931/http://www.cra.ca/en/home/Newsroom/default.aspx Corporate Research Associates]\n| 28\n| {{Party shading/NDP (Canada)}}| '''37'''\n| 31\n| 3\n|-\n| Feb 2009\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20071213043931/http://www.cra.ca/en/home/Newsroom/default.aspx Corporate Research Associates]\n| 30\n| {{Party shading/NDP (Canada)}}| '''36'''\n| 31\n| 3\n|-\n| Nov 2008\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20071213043931/http://www.cra.ca/en/home/Newsroom/default.aspx Corporate Research Associates]\n| 33\n| {{Party shading/NDP (Canada)}}| '''37'''\n| 27\n| 3\n|-\n| Aug 2008\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20071213043931/http://www.