y Davis \n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[William H. Langille|Bill Langille]] \u2020\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Cumberland North]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Ernie Fage]] \n|\n|Kim Cail \n|\n|Bruce Alan Fage \n|\n|Darryl Whetter \n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Ernie Fage]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Cumberland South]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Murray Scott]] \n|\n|Andrew Kernohan \n|\n|Mary Dee MacPherson \n|\n|James Dessart \n|\n|David Raymond Amos \n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Murray Scott]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Hants East]]\n|\n|Wayne Fiander \n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[John MacDonell (Nova Scotia politician)|John MacDonell]] \n|\n|[[Malcolm A. MacKay]] \n|\n|Michael Hartlan \n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[John MacDonell (Nova Scotia politician)|John MacDonell]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Truro-Bible Hill]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Jamie Muir (politician)|Jamie Muir]] \n|\n|Jim Harpell \n|\n|Ron Chisholm \n|\n|Barton Cutten \n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Jamie Muir (politician)|Jamie Muir]]\n|}\n\n===Central Halifax===\n{{Canadian politics/candlist header|province=NS|PC|NDP|Liberal|Green|Independent}}\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Halifax Chebucto]]\n|\n|Sean Phillips\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Howard Epstein]]\n|\n|Peter Verner\n|\n|Christopher Harborne\n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Howard Epstein]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Halifax Citadel (electoral district)|Halifax Citadel]]\n|\n|[[Bill Black (businessman)|Bill Black]] \n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP|background}}|\n|[[Leonard Preyra]] \n|\n|Devin Maxwell \n|\n|'''[[Nick Wright (politician)|Nick Wright]]'''\n|\n|\n|\n|Vacant\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Halifax Clayton Park]]\n|\n|[[Mary Ann McGrath]] \n|\n|Linda Power \n|{{Canadian party col