an party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[David Wilson (Canadian politician)|David Wilson]] \n|\n|Todd Pettigrew \n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[David Wilson (Canadian politician)|Dave Wilson]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Inverness (provincial electoral district)|Inverness]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|'''[[Rodney MacDonald]]'''\n|\n|Tim Murphy \n|\n|Mary MacLennan \n|\n|John Gibson \n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Rodney MacDonald]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Richmond (Nova Scotia provincial electoral district)|Richmond]]\n|\n|John Greene \n|\n|Mary Pat Cude \n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Michel Samson]] \n|\n|Noreen Hartlen \n|\n|\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Michel Samson]]\n|-\n|bgcolor=whitesmoke|[[Victoria-The Lakes]]\n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC|background}}|\n|[[Keith Bain]] \n|\n|Joan O'Liari \n|\n|[[Gerald Sampson]] \n|\n|Michelle Smith \n|\n|Stemer MacLeod \n|{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal|background}}|\n|[[Gerald Sampson]]\n|}\n\n==Opinion polls==\n{|Class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:85%;line-height:13px\"\n|- style=\"height:30px; background-color:#E9E9E9\"\n! style=\"width:100px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Date\n! style=\"width:200px;\" rowspan=\"2\"| Source\n! style=\"width:70px;\"| [[Progressive Conservative Association of Nova Scotia|PC]]\n! style=\"width:70px;\"| [[Nova Scotia New Democratic Party|NDP]]\n! style=\"width:70px;\"| [[Nova Scotia Liberal Party|Liberal]]\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{Canadian party colour|NS|PC}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{Canadian party colour|NS|NDP}};\"|\n! style=\"background:{{Canadian party colour|NS|Liberal}};\"|\n|-\n| 5 Jun 2006\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20071213043931/http://www.cra.ca/en/home/Newsroom/default.aspx Corporate Research Associates]\n| {{Party shading/Conservative (Canada)}}| '''38'''\n| 36\n| 20\n|-\n| 23 May 2006\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/2007